2007年瑞士聯邦選舉中，[[右翼|右翼]]政黨[[瑞士人民黨|瑞士人民黨]]取得29%國會議席（62席下議院、7席上議院）是自[[一戰|一戰]]以來右翼政黨取得的最高百分比。人民黨早於2003年聯邦選舉中成功取得國會第一大黨地位<ref>{{cite news| title=Contradictions in Swiss Election| url=http://ap.google.com/article/ALeqM5hpAvn0WwnT8Keo7AzaY3d1GcGD6g| accessdate=2007-10-25| publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]| author=Alexander H. Higgins| language=en| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071115003152/http://ap.google.com/article/ALeqM5hpAvn0WwnT8Keo7AzaY3d1GcGD6g| archivedate=2007-11-15}}</ref>該黨一直反對[[歐盟|歐盟]]，被視為鼓吹種族主義和仇外，競選期間該黨一張海報中，一隻白色綿羊將一隻黑色綿羊踢出[[瑞士國旗|瑞士國旗]]以外，被聯合國批評。<ref>{{cite news |title=Right-Wing People's Party Win Swiss Elections |url=http://www.dw-world.de/dw/article/0,2144,2834523,00.html |publisher=Deutsche Welle |date=2007-10-22 |accessdate=2007-10-26 |language=en |archive-date=2009-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090703073245/http://www.dw-world.de/dw/article/0,2144,2834523,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>反種族偏狹歐洲委員會（European Commission against Racism and Intolerance）在2003年提到瑞士的仇外事件，包括警察對少數族裔的歧視，及社會對非洲和尋求庇護的[[難民|難民]]等群體不容忍的態度。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Third report on Switzerland |url=http://www.coe.int/t/e/human_rights/ecri/1%2Decri/2%2Dcountry%2Dby%2Dcountry_approach/switzerland/third%20report%20Switzerland%20-%20cri04-5.pdf |accessdate=2007-10-25 |publisher=European Commission against Racism and Intolerance |date=2003-06-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040322141950/http://www.coe.int/t/e/human_rights/ecri/1-ecri/2-country-by-country_approach/switzerland/third%20report%20Switzerland%20-%20cri04-5.pdf |archivedate=2004-03-22 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

=== 非洲 ===
由於非洲各國曾遭受歐洲列強殖民，因此各國獨立後的領土與疆界劃分參差不齊，部分的[[土著|土著]]及[[遊牧民族|遊牧民族]]曾爆發了跨國界衝突和屠殺事件，如[[盧安達大屠殺|盧安達大屠殺]]、[[達爾富爾衝突|達爾富爾衝突]]等等。

